        <publisher value="Patient Care Work Group"/>
        <description value="This profile sets additional expectations for the US Core Condition profile to record, search, and fetch condition or diagnosis terms representing hepatitis B conditions associated with a patient. In addition to the requirements set in the US Core Condition profile, conditionCode is bound to a hepatitis B condition or diagnosis value set. The Condition.onset is set to &quot;must support&quot; and Condition.recordedDate is required."/>
